      "sc:description": "A Fast and Accurate Exhaustive Higher-Order Epistasis Search.\n\nBitEpi: An exhaustive search of higher-order epistatic interactions.\n\nBitEpi is software for an exhaustive search of higher-order epistatic interactions between genomic variants (SNPs) given a binary phenotype (Case/Control).\n\nBitEpi performs an exhaustive search that means it tests all possible combinations of SNPs. For example, the 4-SNP search of 50 SNPs (data.csv) requires to test all \"4 out of 50\" 4-SNP combinations (230300 4-SNP combinations)",
